\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{\alpha}a_{\alpha}x^{\alpha}+\sum_{\alpha}b_{\alpha}x^{\alpha}=\sum_{\alpha}(a_{\alpha}+b_{\alpha})x^{\alpha}$
